  "text": "At the moment we know little about relations between IUT and nonabelian representation-theoretic aspects of the Langlands programme. I expect that more links between the two theories will eventually be found, and, in particular, that the two-dimensional adelic theory of [CITATION_1] and its nonabelian extensions can serve as a bridge between them.",
